spans.text: you grisly shade , Her stony eyeballs staring wide
floating on his watery bier he lies ; " Pale are his cheeks , where Love was wont to play , " And closed those radiant eyes , that late outshone the day . "
When lo ! the bleeding corpse appeared , By savage rocks
were you , Nymphs , OH tell me where , Daughters of Nereus , fresh and fair
the unburied dead , And pale diseases
the unburied dead , And pale diseases shivering
few , whom poisonous Pestilence spares , Of moody madness die , and heart-distracting fears
Anon the crazy bark is born , Of winds , and waves , and rocks the scorn , For Reason shrinks appalled , and trembling quits the helm
dreadful on the iron bed , The purple Furies grind their cankered teeth
chaos dark and dread , Bad Discord
